---
import "@fontsource/poppins/500.css";
import "@fontsource/poppins/400.css";
---

<!-- Hello Gamers! -->
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <!-- Meta tags for SEO -->
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="CrunchyCode Games is an independent game studio specializing in immersive and entertaining experiences for gamers."
    />
    <meta
      name="keywords"
      content="CrunchyCode Games, The Quest of the Tiny Hero, RPG, Independent Game Studio"
    />
    <meta name="author" content="CrunchyCode Games" />
    <!-- Open Graph metadata for social sharing -->
    <meta
      property="og:title"
      content="CrunchyCode Games - Independent Game Studio"
    />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="We specialize in creating immersive and entertaining gaming experiences."
    />
    <meta property="og:image" content="game.png" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.crunchycodegames.com/game" />
    <!-- Canonical URL -->
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.crunchycodegames.com/game" />
    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" href="../img/favicon.svg" />
    <title>CrunchyCode Games - Independent Game Studio</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="flex min-h-screen w-screen flex-col gap-16 items-center bg-neutral-100">
      <nav
        class="bg-rose-600 sticky top-0 w-screen px-5 py-5 text-white lg:shadow-xl"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 justify-between container lg:px-20 mx-auto"
        >
          <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
            <img class="h-14 lg:h-8" src="img/logo.svg" />
            <h1 class="text-center text-6xl lg:text-2xl font-medium">
              CrunchyCode Games
            </h1>
          </div>
          <ul
            class="flex items-end justify-center gap-5 font-medium text-4xl lg:text-xl"
          >
            <li>
              <a
                href="/"
                class="transition-opacity duration-200 ease-in-out hover:opacity-80"
                >Home</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href="/tqotth/"
                class="transition-opacity duration-200 ease-in-out hover:opacity-80"
                >The Quest of the Tiny Hero</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href="/pd/"
                class="transition-opacity duration-200 ease-in-out hover:opacity-80"
                >PolyDestroyer</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a class="hidden lg:block" href="/hosting/">
                <span
                  class="px-3 py-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-colors ease-in-out drop-shadow-lg"
                >
                  View our <b>new</b> Web Hosting!
                </span>
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <section class="sticky top-[205px] lg:hidden bg-indigo-600 w-screen h-28 -mt-32 flex justify-center items-center text-white text-5xl">
        <a href="/hosting/">
            View our <b>new</b> Web Hosting!
        </a>
      </section>

      <section class="flex w-3/4 lg:w-1/2 flex-col items-center pt-28 lg:pt-0">
        <h1 class="text-center text-6xl lg:text-5xl text-gray-900 font-medium lg:leading-snug">
          The <span class="text-rose-600">Quest of the Tiny Hero</span>
        </h1>
      </section>


      <section class="flex flex-col lg:justify-between lg:flex-row w-3/4 lg:w-3/4 items-center text-center lg:text-xl text-5xl gap-10 lg:gap-0 pt-28 lg:pt-0">
        <div class="w-full lg:mr-10 lg:text-right lg:text-justify">
          Embark on an epic journey in "The Quest of The Tiny Hero," a captivating 2D top-down RPG that invites players into a world teeming with vibrant life and boundless adventure. Designed to charm with its pixel-art visuals and enchant players with its RPG mechanics, this title is a love letter to the classic role-playing games that have enchanted us for decades.
        </div>

        <div class="w-full lg:ml-10 text-center">
          <img class="mt-4 shadow-solid hover:shadow-solid-lg transition-shadow ease-in-out" src="/img/tqotth1.png" />
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:justify-between lg:flex-row w-3/4 lg:w-3/4 items-center text-center lg:text-xl text-5xl gap-10 lg:gap-0 pt-28 lg:pt-0 border-t-8 lg:border-0">
        <div class="w-full lg:mr-10">
          <img class="mt-4 shadow-solid hover:shadow-solid-lg transition-shadow ease-in-out" src="/img/tqotth2.gif" />
        </div>

        <div class="w-full lg:ml-10 lg:text-left lg:text-justify">
          "The Quest of The Tiny Hero" is an accessible entry into the RPG genre that offers a fulfilling adventure for both newcomers and seasoned players. Can you rise from the diminutive stature of an aspiring hero to become the titan your village needs? Your quest awaits.
        </div>
      </section>


      <footer
        class="text-center text-4xl lg:text-base w-screen text-white bg-rose-600 p-5"
      >
        <p class="mb-2">
          <a
            class="text-white hover:text-gray-300 underline transition-colors duration-200 ease-in-out"
            href="terms">Terms and conditions</a
          ><a
            class="text-white hover:text-gray-300 underline transition-colors duration-200 ease-in-out"
            href="privacy">Privacy Policy</a
          >
        </p>
        <p>
          &copy; 2023 - 2024 CrunchyCode Games Ltd. - All rights reserved.
          Company No. - 15211638.
        </p>
      </footer>
    </main>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  main {
    /* use the logo as a background image */
    background-image: url("/img/logo.svg");
    background-repeat: repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }
</style>
